N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 22 ยง 28.14 - General power of court

State Regulations

The court where the action was commenced
or, if the action was transferred, the court to which it was transferred, shall
hear and determine all collateral motions relating to arbitration
proceedings. Notes
